text:
Don’t try to compete with Jennifer Lopez! Or you could end up single. That’s the message the “El Anillo” singer sent her boyfriend Alex Rodriguez on Jimmy Kimmel Live.

Watch the video above to find out the one thing Alex should never do if he wants to stay with Jennifer!
title: Jennifer Lopez Says Her Relationship With Alex Rodriguez 'Is Over' If He Does This One Thing
